scripts.script:
(do
  (def! m 8)
  (def! l (. shape :left))
  (def! r (. shape :right))
  (def! t (. shape :top))
  (def! b (. shape :bottom))
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. shape :renderDefault canvas)
  (. canvas :line (- r 8) t (- r 8) b seed)
  (. canvas :setFillColor (. shape :strokeColor) seed)
  (. canvas :fillRect (- r 8) t r (- b (/ (. shape :height) 2)) seed))

(do
  (def! l (. shape :left))
  (def! r (. shape :right))
  (def! t (. shape :top))
  (def! b (. shape :bottom))
  (def! w (. shape :width))
  (def! h (. shape :height))
  (def! x (/ (+ l r) 2))
  (def! y (/ (+ t b) 2))
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (def! g 10)
  (def! lw (* w 0.15))
  (def! lh (* h 0.15))
  (def! island (. shape :getPropertyValue "Island"))
  (def! landscape (< h w))
  (. canvas :strokeRoundRect l t r b 44)
  (. canvas :strokeRoundRect (- l g) (- t g) (+ r g) (+ b g) 50)
  (if island
    (if landscape
      (. canvas :strokeRoundRect
         (+ l g) (- y lh) (+ l (* g 3)) (+ y lh) g)
      (. canvas :strokeRoundRect
         (- x lw) (+ t g) (+ x lw) (+ t (* g 3)) g))))

(do
  (def! l (. shape :left))
  (def! r (. shape :right))
  (def! t (. shape :top))
  (def! b (. shape :bottom))
  (def! g 10)
  [[(- l g) (- t g)] [(+ r g) (+ b g)]])
